products.name: Star Wars The Mandalorian Action Figure 2-Pack 1/6 The Mandalorian & Blurrg 37 cm
products.description:
"You are a Mandalorian! Your ancestors rode the great Mythosaur. Surely you can ride this young foal."

Returning to the beginning of The Mandalorian's story, Star Wars witnessed the eponymous bounty hunter took on a mysterious bounty from a client to search for an asset on the desert planet of Arvala-7. Upon arrival, Mandalorian was assisted by Kuiil the Ugnaught and learned to ride the blurrg in order to reach the settlement seeking the valuable asset.

Fans were instantly captivated by the unfolding of the Mandalorian's journey, and in celebration of Star Wars Day, Sideshow and Hot Toys is excited to present a special 1:6th scale collectible set featuring the Mandalorian in his original armor and the Blurrg!

The Mandalorian collectible figure features meticulously crafted helmet and armor pieces, a finely tailored outfit, detailed weathering effects, a blaster rifle, a blaster pistol, and a display base.

The highly accurate Blurrg is skillfully developed based on the appearance of the creature in The Mandalorian. Standing at approximately 37 cm tall (43 cm with base) and 60 cm in length, it features a greatly detailed head and body, articulated arms, a saddle, and a rocky theme display stand!

This Mandalorian and Blurrg Sixth Scale Collectible Set will be an amazing piece for your special Star Wars collection!

products.name: Naruto Shippuden Jiraiya One Last Heartbeat HQS 1/8 Statue Tsume Art 60 cm (New)
products.description:
Naruto ShippudenStatue ofJiraiya One Last Heartbeat, 1/8 scale size approx.60cm.Official productinlimited edition of 2750 piecesbyTsume.

The Great lord Elder prophesied that I would be the one to guide the revolution. A person who would make a great choice that will bring either peace or destruction to the world of the shinobi.

An epic moment that we decided to immortalize through the realization of a 1/8 HQS statue by Tsume, paying tribute to the heroic legendary ninja! Very dynamic, the statue emphasises the intense emotion felt in the heart of the action, like a freeze frame: that of one ultimate heartbeat, a last will that will change the course of the future ...

The scene takes place in Nagatos original village : Ame, the Village Hidden in the Rain. Indeed, behind the rock plate where Jiraiya is agonizing, we find imposing line pipe and grids, covered with a metallic paint mixing copper, brown, black and gray shades for a realistic rendering. Under the effect of the 5 ninjas powerful attack, the water in bluish transparent resin is unleashing, creating scum. The legendary ninja begins what he thinks to be his ultimate fight: the time of his great choice has come! Determined to unmask Pain, he recognizes Yahiko, one of his former students having lost his live. As Tend, he wears Pains violet ring on his thumb and takes the role of leader, being above the 4 other ninjas.

These former shinobis were all once defeated by Jiraiya. They wear the long black robe with the Akatsuki symbol, painted with black, gray and dark red shades, then covered with a matte varnish to be faithful to the license. Their hair is painted in a gradient of light and darker orange while their barred headband indicates that they have deserted the Village Hidden in the Rain. Their pupils are formed of gray and purple concentric circles ... The djutsu Rinnegan ... Nagato! The dozens of metal piercings implanted in the corpses of the ninjas, serve as emitters and receivers of chakra, allowing Nagato to remotely control them ... While Jiraiya finally gets his answer, 5 spears pierce his back, staining his long white hair with blood. Lying in a pool of his own blood, in reddish and varnished transparent resin, the condemned ninja remembers Narutos unwavering determination ... A memory allowing his heart to beat one last time to finally carry out his mission. Grimacing with his bloody mouth, showing a glassy but determined look, he uses the chakra in bluish transparent resin emanating from his fingertip, to engrave a coded message on Fukasakus back. Here, we notice his arm pierced by the spear of the 6th Pain he killed. The toad, just like Jiraiya, shows an expression of both pain and obstinacy: it became the key to stop Pain, ready to deliver this crucial message ... While Jiraiya is slowly dying, the 5 Pain pounce on him to put a definitive end to his life, their robe thrown back due to the speed of movement.

His duty accomplished, the legendary ninja lets himself be serenely dragged to the abyssal depths. Jiraiyas last thoughts are about his next novel, which he decides to call "The Story of Naruto Uzumaki", because he is absolutely sure now : here is the Child of the Prophecy!

The statue comes with a numbered plate and a certificate of authenticity.

Total run of 2,750 pieces.

Dimensions: L: 59.5 cm; W: 55.7 cm; D: 49.6 cm

products.name: Naruto Statue 1/4 Orochimaru BIJUtsu by Tsume 53cm
products.description:
NarutoStatue ofOrochimaruinBIJUtsu collection,1/4 scale size approx.53cm.Official productinlimited edition of 800 piecesbyTsume Art.

Part of Sasukes destiny, Orochimaru is depicted here during his battle against Sarutobi on the rooftops of Konoha, sword in hand. An essential piece for dedicated collectors! Orochimarus face is enhanced with the use of transparent resin for his eyes, a technique that brings a fascinating depth to his piercing gaze. His menacing and calculating expression is captured with great precision, making this Orochimaru statue particularly lifelike and striking. The serpent adds to the threatening atmosphere of the statue. This Naruto statue highlights Orochimarus reptilian connection with a serpent sculpted in meticulous detail, mouth open, its dynamic pose reinforcing the dangerous nature of the character.

The base represents the rooftops of Konoha during Orochimarus battle with Sarutobi. Every detail has been carefully crafted to elevate the entire piece. The edge of the base symbolizes Sasuke's destiny, as seen in all statues of the Crossed Destinies Collection. A symbol of Orochimaru's cursed mark can also be placed on the base.

Eyes in Resin

The eyes of various characters from the BIJUtsu range are made from transparent resin, giving an exceptional depth to their gaze.

Paint Style

In our Crossed Destinies, weve added a subtle cell-shading effect, visible from a specific angle of the statue. This allows to provide depth and a certain dynamism to the statue.

Base

Depending on the destiny of Naruto or Sasuke, the base varies, telling the story of each protagonist.

Display Set

The BIJUtsu Display Set transforms your box into an elegant display stand. The Cover enhances your statue, and the Scroll decorates the background, adding charm to your space.

*32cm x 32cm x 53cm

products.name: Naruto Statue 1/6 Tsunade Ikigai by Tsume 46cm
products.description:
Narutostatue ofTsunadeinIkigai collection,1/6 scale size approx.46cm.Official productinlimited edition of 599 piecesbyTsume Art.

-LEGENDARY SANNIN-

Tsunade, one of the three legendary Sannin of Konoha, represents the strength and wisdom of this iconic trio alongside Jiraiya and Orochimaru. As an expert in medical techniques and possessing immense physical power, she is a symbol of invincibility, both as a protector and a fierce warrior. This statue captures her aura and determination in a powerful attack pose.

-KATSUYU-

By her side stands Katsuyu, the giant slug Tsunade summons during battles. Katsuyu is not only a defensive ally but also crucial in healing comrades and dealing damage to enemies. The duo is depicted here at their full strength, ready to fight and protect, a perfect combination of force and strategy.

-MARKS OF REGENERATION-

Tsunades statue highlights the distinctive marks on her forehead, a symbol of her mastery over the Strength of a Hundred Seal. This ultimate technique allows her to heal instantly and serves as a reminder of her pivotal role as a medical ninja. The detailed sculpt showcases these marks, emphasizing the immense power within her, ready to be unleashed.

18 X 36 X 46 CM

products.name: Naruto Statue 1/6 Jiraiya Ikigai by Tsume 43cm
products.description:
Narutostatue ofJiraiyainIkigai collection,1/6 scale size approx.43cm.Official productinlimited edition of 899 piecesbyTsume Art.

-LEGENDARY SANNIN-

One of the most respected and powerful ninjas of Konoha, Jiraiya is part of the legendary Sannin, a mythical trio formed alongside Orochimaru and Tsunade. Depicted here in a dynamic stance, Jiraiya embodies the perfect balance between raw strength and wisdom.

-SAGE MODE-

In this scene, Jiraiya is shown fully mastering Sage Mode, a rare and powerful technique learned at Mount Myboku alongside the wise toads, Fukasaku and Shima, who are featured by his side. This transformation allows him to amplify his strength, speed, and sensory abilities. A perfect embodiment of the harmony between man and nature, this statue highlights the serenity and immense power he draws from this mode.

-SENPO GOEMON-

This Ikigai depicts Jiraiya in his battle against Pain. Jiraiya spits oil, Fukasaku generates wind, and Shima breathes fire, creating a true wave of burning, destructive oil. The toads are intricately sculpted, adding dynamism and realism to the scene, while the oil gushes around him, bringing the action to life. This statue captures all the intensity and grandeur of the fight, paying homage to this unparalleled ninja.

22 X 37 X 43 CM
